{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778730034666,"sessionID":"ses_1db6e3a79ffefCAEjX4WmRwXGO","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_ZK1PHbydd37N8VAfCGDfyimw","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\skill-library\\bilibili-all-in-one-1.0.12\\SKILL.md","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\skill-library\\bilibili-all-in-one-1.0.12\\skill.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: name: bilibili-all-in-one\n3: description: >\n4:   A comprehensive Bilibili toolkit that integrates hot trending monitoring,\n5:   video downloading, video watching/playback, subtitle downloading,\n6:   and video publishing capabilities into a single unified skill.\n7:   Supports Bilibili session cookie authentication for publishing and\n8:   high-quality downloads. Requests go to official Bilibili API endpoints\n9:   and YouTube oEmbed API (for YouTube stats) over HTTPS.\n10: version: 1.0.12\n11: type: code\n12: implementation: python\n13: interface: cli-and-api\n14: runtime: python>=3.8\n15: languages:\n16:   - zh-CN\n17:   - en\n18: tags:\n19:   - bilibili\n20:   - video-download\n21:   - hot-trending\n22:   - subtitle\n23:   - danmaku\n24:   - video-publish\n25:   - video-player\n26:   - youtube-stats\n27:   - batch-download\n28:   - multi-format\n29: author: wscats\n30: license: MIT\n31: homepage: https://github.com/wscats/bilibili-all-in-one\n32: repository: https://github.com/wscats/bilibili-all-in-one\n33: entry_point: main.py\n34: required_env_vars:\n35:   - BILIBILI_SESSDATA\n36:   - BILIBILI_BILI_JCT\n37: optional_env_vars:\n38:   - BILIBILI_BUVID3\n39: install: pip install -r requirements.txt\n40: ---\n41: \n42: # Bilibili All-in-One Skill\n43: \n44: A comprehensive Bilibili toolkit that integrates hot trending monitoring, video downloading, video watching/playback, subtitle downloading, and video publishing capabilities into a single unified skill.\n45: \n46: > **⚠️ Required Environment Variables:** `BILIBILI_SESSDATA`, `BILIBILI_BILI_JCT` (required), `BILIBILI_BUVID3` (optional)\n47: > These are sensitive Bilibili session cookies needed for authenticated operations (publishing, high-quality downloads).\n48: > Features that do NOT require authentication: hot monitoring, standard-quality downloads, subtitle listing, danmaku, stats viewing.\n49: >\n50: > **📦 Install:** `pip install -r requirements.txt` (all standard PyPI packages: httpx, bilibili-api-python, aiohttp, beautifulsoup4, lxml, requests)\n51: >\n52: > **🔗 Source:** [github.com/wscats/bilibili-all-in-one](https://github.com/wscats/bilibili-all-in-one)\n53: \n54: ---\n55: ### 何时激活\n56: \n57: 当用户说出或暗示以下内容时，本 Skill 会被激活：\n58: \n59: | 触发场景 | 匹配的模块 | 典型触发词 |\n60: |---|---|---|\n61: | 查看B站热门、热搜、排行榜、必看榜 | 🔥 Hot Monitor | \"热门\"、\"热搜\"、\"排行\"、\"趋势\"、\"必看\"、\"流行\"、\"榜单\" |\n62: | 下载B站视频、提取音频、批量下载 | ⬇️ Downloader | \"下载\"、\"保存视频\"、\"提取音频\"、\"导出MP4\"、\"批量下载\" |\n63: | 查看视频播放量、点赞数、数据追踪、对比 | 👀 Watcher | \"播放量\"、\"点赞\"、\"数据\"、\"统计\"、\"对比\"、\"监控\"、\"追踪\"、\"观看量\" |\n64: | 下载字幕、转换字幕格式、合并字幕 | 📝 Subtitle | \"字幕\"、\"CC\"、\"SRT\"、\"ASS\"、\"字幕下载\"、\"字幕转换\"、\"翻译\" |\n65: | 播放视频、获取弹幕、播放列表 | ▶️ Player | \"播放\"、\"弹幕\"、\"播放地址\"、\"分P\"、\"播放列表\"、\"danmaku\" |\n66: | 上传视频、发布、定时发布、草稿、编辑、删除 | 📤 Publisher | \"上传\"、\"发布\"、\"投稿\"、\"定时发布\"、\"草稿\"、\"编辑视频\"、\"删除视频\" |\n67: | 涉及YouTube视频数据查询 | 👀 Watcher | \"YouTube\"、\"油管\"、\"YTB\"、\"YouTube观看量\" |\n68: | 提及B站链接或BV号 | 自动识别 | `BV*`、`bilibili.com/video/*`、`b23.tv/*` |\n69: \n70: > 💡 **提示**：只要用户消息中包含 B站/Bilibili 相关操作意图，或包含 BV 号、bilibili 链接，本 Skill 即会被自动激活。无需显式声明调用。\n71: \n72: ---\n73: \n74: ## Features\n75: | Module | Description |\n76: |---|---|\n77: | 🔥 **Hot Monitor** | Monitor Bilibili hot/trending videos and topics in real-time |\n78: | ⬇️ **Downloader** | Download Bilibili videos with multiple quality and format options |\n79: | 👀 **Watcher** | Watch and track video engagement metrics (supports Bilibili & YouTube) |\n80: | 📝 **Subtitle** | Download and process subtitles in multiple formats and languages |\n81: | ▶️ **Player** | Get playback URLs, danmaku (bullet comments), and playlist info |\n82: | 📤 **Publisher** | Upload, schedule, edit, and manage videos on Bilibili |\n83: \n84: ## Installation\n85: \n86: ### Requirements\n87: \n88: - Python >= 3.8\n89: - ffmpeg (optional, for merging video/audio streams)\n90: \n91: ### Install Dependencies\n92: \n93: ```bash\n94: pip install -r requirements.txt\n95: ```\n96: \n97: ### Dependencies\n98: \n99: - `httpx >= 0.24.0`\n100: - `bilibili-api-python >= 16.0.0`\n101: - `aiohttp >= 3.8.0`\n102: - `beautifulsoup4 >= 4.12.0`\n103: - `lxml >= 4.9.0`\n104: - `requests >= 2.31.0`\n105: \n106: ## Configuration\n107: \n108: Some features (downloading high-quality videos, publishing, etc.) require Bilibili authentication. You can provide credentials in three ways:\n109: \n110: ### 1. Environment Variables\n111: \n112: ```bash\n113: export BILIBILI_SESSDATA=\"your_sessdata\"\n114: export BILIBILI_BILI_JCT=\"your_bili_jct\"\n115: export BILIBILI_BUVID3=\"your_buvid3\"\n116: ```\n117: \n118: ### 2. Credential File\n119: \n120: Create a JSON file (e.g., `credentials.json`):\n121: \n122: ```json\n123: {\n124:   \"sessdata\": \"your_sessdata\",\n125:   \"bili_jct\": \"your_bili_jct\",\n126:   \"buvid3\": \"your_buvid3\"\n127: }\n128: ```\n129: \n130: ### 3. Direct Parameters\n131: \n132: Pass credentials directly when initializing:\n133: \n134: ```python\n135: from main import BilibiliAllInOne\n136: \n137: app = BilibiliAllInOne(\n138:     sessdata=\"your_sessdata\",\n139:     bili_jct=\"your_bili_jct\",\n140:     buvid3=\"your_buvid3\",\n141: )\n142: ```\n143: \n144: > **How to get cookies:** Log in to [bilibili.com](https://www.bilibili.com), open browser DevTools (F12) → Application → Cookies, and copy the values of `SESSDATA`, `bili_jct`, and `buvid3`.\n145: \n146: ## ⚠️ Security & Privacy\n147: \n148: ### Credential Handling\n149: \n150: This skill handles **sensitive Bilibili session cookies**. Please read the following carefully:\n151: \n152: | Concern | Detail |\n153: |---|---|\n154: | **What credentials are needed?** | `SESSDATA`, `bili_jct`, `buvid3` — Bilibili browser cookies |\n155: | **Which features require authentication?** | Publishing (upload/edit/delete/schedule/draft), downloading 1080p+/4K quality videos |\n156: | **Which features work WITHOUT credentials?** | Hot monitoring, standard-quality downloads, subtitle listing, danmaku fetching, stats viewing |\n157: | **Where are credentials sent?** | To official Bilibili API endpoints (`api.bilibili.com`, `member.bilibili.com`) over HTTPS. YouTube metadata uses `www.youtube.com/oembed` (no credentials sent) |\n158: | **Are credentials persisted to disk?** | **NO** — unless you explicitly call `auth.save_to_file()`. Credentials stay in memory by default |\n159: | **File permissions for saved credentials** | `0600` (owner read/write only) — restrictive by default |\n160: \n161: ### Best Practices\n162: \n163: 1. 🧪 **Use a test account** — Do NOT provide your primary Bilibili account cookies for evaluation/testing purposes.\n164: 2. 🔒 **Prefer in-memory credentials** — Pass credentials via environment variables or direct parameters rather than saving to a file.\n165: 3. 📁 **If you must save credentials** — Use `auth.save_to_file()` which creates files with `0600` permissions. Delete the file when no longer needed.\n166: 4. 🐳 **Run in isolation** — When possible, run this skill in an isolated container/environment and inspect network traffic.\n167: 5. 🌐 **Verify network traffic** — All HTTP requests go to Bilibili's official domains and YouTube oEmbed API only. You can verify by monitoring outbound connections.\n168: 6. ❌ **No exfiltration** — This skill does NOT send credentials to any third-party service, analytics endpoint, or telemetry server.\n169: \n170: ### Network Endpoints Used\n171: \n172: | Domain | Purpose |\n173: |---|---|\n174: | `api.bilibili.com` | Video info, stats, hot lists, subtitles, danmaku, playback URLs |\n175: | `member.bilibili.com` | Video publishing (upload, edit, delete) |\n176: | `upos-sz-upcdnbda2.bilivideo.com` | Video file upload CDN |\n177: | `www.bilibili.com` | Web page scraping fallback |\n178: | `www.youtube.com` | YouTube video metadata via oEmbed API (no auth required) |\n179: \n180: ### Credential Requirement by Module\n181: \n182: | Module | Auth Required? | Notes |\n183: |---|---|---|\n184: | 🔥 Hot Monitor | ❌ No | All public APIs |\n185: | ⬇️ Downloader | ⚠️ Optional | Required only for 1080p+ / 4K quality |\n186: | 👀 Watcher | ❌ No | Public stats APIs |\n187: | 📝 Subtitle | ❌ No | Public subtitle APIs |\n188: | ▶️ Player | ⚠️ Optional | Required for high-quality playback URLs |\n189: | 📤 Publisher | ✅ **Required** | All operations need `SESSDATA` + `bili_jct` |\n190: \n191: ## Usage\n192: \n193: ### CLI\n194: \n195: ```bash\n196: python main.py <skill_name> <action> [params_json]\n197: ```\n198: \n199: ### Python API\n200: \n201: ```python\n202: import asyncio\n203: from main import BilibiliAllInOne\n204: \n205: app = BilibiliAllInOne()\n206: \n207: async def demo():\n208:     result = await app.execute(\"hot_monitor\", \"get_hot\", limit=5)\n209:     print(result)\n210: \n211: asyncio.run(demo())\n212: ```\n213: \n214: ---\n215: \n216: ## Skills Reference\n217: \n218: ### 1. 🔥 Hot Monitor (`bilibili_hot_monitor`)\n219: \n220: Monitor Bilibili hot/trending videos and topics in real-time. Supports filtering by category, tracking rank changes.\n221: \n222: #### Actions\n223: \n224: | Action | Description | Parameters |\n225: |---|---|---|\n226: | `get_hot` | Get popular/hot videos | `page`, `page_size` |\n227: | `get_trending` | Get trending series/topics | `limit` |\n228: | `get_weekly` | Get weekly must-watch list | `number` (week number, optional) |\n229: | `get_rank` | Get category ranking videos | `category`, `limit` |\n230: \n231: #### Supported Categories\n232: \n233: `all`, `anime`, `music`, `dance`, `game`, `tech`, `life`, `food`, `car`, `fashion`, `entertainment`, `movie`, `tv`\n234: \n235: #### Examples\n236: \n237: ```bash\n238: # Get top 10 hot videos\n239: python main.py hot_monitor get_hot '{\"page_size\": 10}'\n240: \n241: # Get trending topics\n242: python main.py hot_monitor get_trending '{\"limit\": 5}'\n243: \n244: # Get this week's must-watch\n245: python main.py hot_monitor get_weekly\n246: \n247: # Get game category rankings\n248: python main.py hot_monitor get_rank '{\"category\": \"game\", \"limit\": 10}'\n249: ```\n250: \n251: ```python\n252: # Python API\n253: result = await app.execute(\"hot_monitor\", \"get_hot\", page_size=10)\n254: result = await app.execute(\"hot_monitor\", \"get_rank\", category=\"game\", limit=10)\n255: ```\n256: \n257: ---\n258: \n259: ### 2. ⬇️ Downloader (`bilibili_downloader`)\n260: \n261: Download Bilibili videos with support for multiple quality options, batch downloading, and format selection.\n262: \n263: #### Actions\n264: \n265: | Action | Description | Parameters |\n266: |---|---|---|\n267: | `get_info` | Get video information | `url` |\n268: | `get_formats` | List available qualities/formats | `url` |\n269: | `download` | Download a single video | `url`, `quality`, `output_dir`, `format`, `page` |\n270: | `batch_download` | Download multiple videos | `urls`, `quality`, `output_dir`, `format` |\n271: \n272: #### Quality Options\n273: \n274: `360p`, `480p`, `720p`, `1080p` (default), `1080p+`, `4k`\n275: \n276: #### Format Options\n277: \n278: `mp4` (default), `flv`, `mp3` (audio only)\n279: \n280: #### Examples\n281: \n282: ```bash\n283: # Get video info\n284: python main.py downloader get_info '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n285: \n286: # List available formats\n287: python main.py downloader get_formats '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n288: \n289: # Download in 1080p MP4\n290: python main.py downloader download '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"quality\": \"1080p\", \"format\": \"mp4\"}'\n291: \n292: # Extract audio only\n293: python main.py downloader download '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"format\": \"mp3\"}'\n294: \n295: # Batch download\n296: python main.py downloader batch_download '{\"urls\": [\"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"BV1yy411c8nE\"], \"quality\": \"720p\"}'\n297: ```\n298: \n299: ```python\n300: # Python API\n301: info = await app.execute(\"downloader\", \"get_info\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n302: result = await app.execute(\"downloader\", \"download\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\", quality=\"1080p\")\n303: ```\n304: \n305: ---\n306: \n307: ### 3. 👀 Watcher (`bilibili_watcher`)\n308: \n309: Watch and monitor Bilibili (and YouTube) videos. Track view counts, comments, likes, and other engagement metrics over time.\n310: \n311: #### Actions\n312: \n313: | Action | Description | Parameters |\n314: |---|---|---|\n315: | `watch` | Get detailed video information | `url` |\n316: | `get_stats` | Get current engagement statistics | `url` |\n317: | `track` | Track metrics over time | `url`, `interval` (minutes), `duration` (hours) |\n318: | `compare` | Compare multiple videos | `urls` |\n319: \n320: #### Supported Platforms\n321: \n322: - **Bilibili**: `https://www.bilibili.com/video/BVxxxxxx` or `BVxxxxxx`\n323: - **YouTube**: `https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xxxxx` or `https://youtu.be/xxxxx`\n324: \n325: #### Examples\n326: \n327: ```bash\n328: # Get video details\n329: python main.py watcher watch '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n330: \n331: # Get current stats\n332: python main.py watcher get_stats '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n333: \n334: # Track views every 30 minutes for 12 hours\n335: python main.py watcher track '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"interval\": 30, \"duration\": 12}'\n336: \n337: # Compare multiple videos\n338: python main.py watcher compare '{\"urls\": [\"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"BV1yy411c8nE\"]}'\n339: ```\n340: \n341: ```python\n342: # Python API\n343: details = await app.execute(\"watcher\", \"watch\", url=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ\")\n344: comparison = await app.execute(\"watcher\", \"compare\", urls=[\"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"BV1yy411c8nE\"])\n345: ```\n346: \n347: ---\n348: \n349: ### 4. 📝 Subtitle (`bilibili_subtitle`)\n350: \n351: Download and process subtitles/CC from Bilibili videos. Supports multiple subtitle formats and languages.\n352: \n353: #### Actions\n354: \n355: | Action | Description | Parameters |\n356: |---|---|---|\n357: | `list` | List available subtitles | `url` |\n358: | `download` | Download subtitles | `url`, `language`, `format`, `output_dir` |\n359: | `convert` | Convert subtitle format | `input_path`, `output_format`, `output_dir` |\n360: | `merge` | Merge multiple subtitle files | `input_paths`, `output_path`, `output_format` |\n361: \n362: #### Supported Formats\n363: \n364: `srt` (default), `ass`, `vtt`, `txt`, `json`\n365: \n366: #### Supported Languages\n367: \n368: `zh-CN` (default), `en`, `ja`, and other language codes available on the video.\n369: \n370: #### Examples\n371: \n372: ```bash\n373: # List available subtitles\n374: python main.py subtitle list '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n375: \n376: # Download Chinese subtitles in SRT format\n377: python main.py subtitle download '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"language\": \"zh-CN\", \"format\": \"srt\"}'\n378: \n379: # Download English subtitles in ASS format\n380: python main.py subtitle download '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"language\": \"en\", \"format\": \"ass\"}'\n381: \n382: # Convert SRT to VTT\n383: python main.py subtitle convert '{\"input_path\": \"./subtitles/video.srt\", \"output_format\": \"vtt\"}'\n384: \n385: # Merge subtitle files\n386: python main.py subtitle merge '{\"input_paths\": [\"part1.srt\", \"part2.srt\"], \"output_path\": \"merged.srt\"}'\n387: ```\n388: \n389: ```python\n390: # Python API\n391: subs = await app.execute(\"subtitle\", \"list\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n392: result = await app.execute(\"subtitle\", \"download\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\", language=\"zh-CN\", format=\"srt\")\n393: ```\n394: \n395: ---\n396: \n397: ### 5. ▶️ Player (`bilibili_player`)\n398: \n399: Play Bilibili videos with support for playback control, playlist management, and danmaku (bullet comments) display.\n400: \n401: #### Actions\n402: \n403: | Action | Description | Parameters |\n404: |---|---|---|\n405: | `play` | Get complete playback info | `url`, `quality`, `page` |\n406: | `get_playurl` | Get direct play URLs | `url`, `quality`, `page` |\n407: | `get_danmaku` | Get danmaku/bullet comments | `url`, `page`, `segment` |\n408: | `get_playlist` | Get playlist/multi-part info | `url` |\n409: \n410: #### Danmaku Modes\n411: \n412: | Mode | Description |\n413: |---|---|\n414: | 1 | Scroll (right to left) |\n415: | 4 | Bottom fixed |\n416: | 5 | Top fixed |\n417: \n418: #### Examples\n419: \n420: ```bash\n421: # Get playback info\n422: python main.py player play '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"quality\": \"1080p\"}'\n423: \n424: # Get direct play URLs\n425: python main.py player get_playurl '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"quality\": \"720p\"}'\n426: \n427: # Get danmaku\n428: python main.py player get_danmaku '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n429: \n430: # Get playlist for multi-part video\n431: python main.py player get_playlist '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n432: \n433: # Get page 3 of a multi-part video\n434: python main.py player play '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"quality\": \"1080p\", \"page\": 3}'\n435: ```\n436: \n437: ```python\n438: # Python API\n439: play_info = await app.execute(\"player\", \"play\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\", quality=\"1080p\")\n440: danmaku = await app.execute(\"player\", \"get_danmaku\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n441: playlist = await app.execute(\"player\", \"get_playlist\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n442: ```\n443: \n444: ---\n445: \n446: ### 6. 📤 Publisher (`bilibili_publisher`)\n447: \n448: Publish videos to Bilibili. Supports uploading videos, setting metadata, scheduling publications, and managing drafts.\n449: \n450: > ⚠️ **Authentication Required**: All publisher actions require valid Bilibili credentials.\n451: \n452: #### Actions\n453: \n454: | Action | Description | Parameters |\n455: |---|---|---|\n456: | `upload` | Upload and publish a video | `file_path`, `title`, `description`, `tags`, `category`, `cover_path`, `dynamic`, `no_reprint`, `open_elec` |\n457: | `draft` | Save as draft | `file_path`, `title`, `description`, `tags`, `category`, `cover_path` |\n458: | `schedule` | Schedule future publication | `file_path`, `title`, `schedule_time`, `description`, `tags`, `category`, `cover_path` |\n459: | `edit` | Edit existing video metadata | `bvid`, `title`, `description`, `tags`, `cover_path` |\n460: | `delete` | Delete a video | `bvid` |\n461: \n462: #### Upload Parameters\n463: \n464: | Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n465: |---|---|---|---|\n466: | `file_path` | string | *required* | Path to the video file |\n467: | `title` | string | *required* | Video title (max 80 chars) |\n468: | `description` | string | `\"\"` | Video description (max 2000 chars) |\n469: | `tags` | string[] | `[\"bilibili\"]` | Tags (max 12, each max 20 chars) |\n470: | `category` | string | `\"171\"` | Category TID |\n471: | `cover_path` | string | `null` | Path to cover image (JPG/PNG) |\n472: | `no_reprint` | int | `1` | 1 = original content, 0 = repost |\n473: | `open_elec` | int | `0` | 1 = enable charging, 0 = disable |\n474: \n475: #### Examples\n476: \n477: ```bash\n478: # Upload and publish\n479: python main.py publisher upload '{\"file_path\": \"./video.mp4\", \"title\": \"My Video\", \"description\": \"Hello World\", \"tags\": [\"test\", \"demo\"], \"category\": \"171\"}'\n480: \n481: # Save as draft\n482: python main.py publisher draft '{\"file_path\": \"./video.mp4\", \"title\": \"Draft Video\"}'\n483: \n484: # Schedule publication\n485: python main.py publisher schedule '{\"file_path\": \"./video.mp4\", \"title\": \"Scheduled Video\", \"schedule_time\": \"2025-12-31T20:00:00+08:00\"}'\n486: \n487: # Edit video metadata\n488: python main.py publisher edit '{\"bvid\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"title\": \"New Title\", \"tags\": [\"updated\"]}'\n489: \n490: # Delete a video\n491: python main.py publisher delete '{\"bvid\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n492: ```\n493: \n494: ```python\n495: # Python API (authentication required)\n496: app = BilibiliAllInOne(sessdata=\"xxx\", bili_jct=\"xxx\", buvid3=\"xxx\")\n497: \n498: result = await app.execute(\"publisher\", \"upload\",\n499:     file_path=\"./video.mp4\",\n500:     title=\"My Video\",\n501:     description=\"Published via bilibili-all-in-one\",\n502:     tags=[\"python\", \"bilibili\"],\n503: )\n504: ```\n505: \n506: ---\n507: \n508: ## Project Structure\n509: \n510: ```\n511: bilibili-all-in-one/\n512: ├── skill.json              # Skill configuration & parameter schema\n513: ├── skill.md                # This documentation file\n514: ├── README.md               # Project README (Chinese)\n515: ├── LICENSE                  # MIT License\n516: ├── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies\n517: ├── .gitignore              # Git ignore rules\n518: ├── main.py                 # Entry point & unified BilibiliAllInOne class\n519: ├── src/\n520: │   ├── __init__.py         # Package exports\n521: │   ├── auth.py             # Authentication & credential management\n522: │   ├── utils.py            # Shared utilities, API constants, helpers\n523: │   ├── hot_monitor.py      # Hot/trending video monitoring\n524: │   ├── downloader.py       # Video downloading\n525: │   ├── watcher.py          # Video watching & stats tracking\n526: │   ├── subtitle.py         # Subtitle downloading & processing\n527: │   ├── player.py           # Video playback & danmaku\n528: │   └── publisher.py        # Video uploading & publishing\n529: └── tests/\n530:     ├── __init__.py\n531:     └── test_all_skill_examples.py  # Comprehensive unit tests\n532: ```\n533: \n534: ## Skill Origin\n535: \n536: This skill integrates the functionality of the following individual skills into one unified toolkit:\n537: \n538: | Original Skill | Source | Integrated Module |\n539: |---|---|---|\n540: | bilibili-hot-monitor | [Jacobzwj/bilibili-hot-monitor](https://clawhub.ai/Jacobzwj/bilibili-hot-monitor) | `hot_monitor` |\n541: | bililidownloader | [caiyundc880518/bililidownloader](https://clawhub.ai/caiyundc880518/bililidownloader) | `downloader` |\n542: | bilibili-youtube-watcher | [donnycui/bilibili-youtube-watcher](https://clawhub.ai/donnycui/bilibili-youtube-watcher) | `watcher` |\n543: | bilibili-subtitle-download-skill | [DavinciEvans/bilibili-subtitle-download-skill](https://clawhub.ai/DavinciEvans/bilibili-subtitle-download-skill) | `subtitle` |\n544: | bilibili-player | [e421083458/bilibili-player](https://clawhub.ai/e421083458/bilibili-player) | `player` |\n545: | bilibili-video-publish | [Johnnyxu820/bilibili-video-publish](https://clawhub.ai/Johnnyxu820/bilibili-video-publish) | `publisher` |\n546: \n547: ## Response Format\n548: \n549: All skill actions return a JSON object with a unified structure:\n550: \n551: ```json\n552: {\n553:   \"success\": true,\n554:   \"...\": \"action-specific fields\"\n555: }\n556: ```\n557: \n558: On error:\n559: \n560: ```json\n561: {\n562:   \"success\": false,\n563:   \"message\": \"Error description\"\n564: }\n565: ```\n566: \n567: ## License\n568: \n569: MIT\n\n(End of file - total 569 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\nname: bilibili-all-in-one\ndescription: >\n  A comprehensive Bilibili toolkit that integrates hot trending monitoring,\n  video downloading, video watching/playback, subtitle downloading,\n  and video publishing capabilities into a single unified skill.\n  Supports Bilibili session cookie authentication for publishing and\n  high-quality downloads. Requests go to official Bilibili API endpoints\n  and YouTube oEmbed API (for YouTube stats) over HTTPS.\nversion: 1.0.12\ntype: code\nimplementation: python\ninterface: cli-and-api\nruntime: python>=3.8\nlanguages:\n  - zh-CN\n  - en\ntags:\n  - bilibili\n  - video-download","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\capability-library\\skill-library\\bilibili-all-in-one-1.0.12\\skill.md","time":{"start":1778730034640,"end":1778730034664}},"id":"prt_e2492606e001NHvhPuqJz9feHg","sessionID":"ses_1db6e3a79ffefCAEjX4WmRwXGO","messageID":"msg_e24924d08001mUoBwDLb7JnZGJ"}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1778730034675,"sessionID":"ses_1db6e3a79ffefCAEjX4WmRwXGO","part":{"id":"prt_e249265eb0017fEyC49HG8wBw5","reason":"tool-calls","messageID":"msg_e24924d08001mUoBwDLb7JnZGJ","sessionID":"ses_1db6e3a79ffefCAEjX4WmRwXGO","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":29993,"input":755,"output":54,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":29184}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1778730040727,"sessionID":"ses_1db6e3a79ffefCAEjX4WmRwXGO","part":{"id":"prt_e24927d95001vGCjMx2FRQrffe","messageID":"msg_e249265ee001acJZjevoyJXRf6","sessionID":"ses_1db6e3a79ffefCAEjX4WmRwXGO","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778730042401,"sessionID":"ses_1db6e3a79ffefCAEjX4WmRwXGO","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_CIt1bTESnLsdQvE5YcPIEPrH","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\skill-library\\bilibili-all-in-one-1.0.12\\README.md","limit":1000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\skill-library\\bilibili-all-in-one-1.0.12\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: \n2: <p align=\"center\">\n3:   <h1 align=\"center\">🎬 Bilibili All-in-One</h1>\n4:   <p align=\"center\">一站式 B站工具箱 — 热门监控 · 视频下载 · 数据追踪 · 字幕提取 · 视频播放 · 投稿发布</p>\n5: </p>\n6: \n7: <p align=\"center\">\n8:   <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/python-%3E%3D3.8-blue?logo=python&logoColor=white\" />\n9:   <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green\" />\n10:   <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.9-orange\" />\n11:   <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/platform-Bilibili%20%7C%20YouTube-pink\" />\n12: </p>\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## 📖 简介\n17: \n18: **Bilibili All-in-One** 是一个综合性的 B站工具包，将 6 个独立的 B站技能整合为一个统一的 Skill，提供从热门监控到视频投稿的全链路能力。\n19: \n20: 支持作为 **AI Agent 技能**、**命令行工具** 或 **Python 库** 使用。\n21: \n22: ## ✨ 功能总览\n23: \n24: | 模块 | 功能 | 是否需要登录 |\n25: |:---:|---|:---:|\n26: | 🔥 **热门监控** | 热门视频、热搜话题、每周必看、分区排行榜 | ❌ |\n27: | ⬇️ **视频下载** | 多清晰度下载、批量下载、格式转换、音频提取 | ⚠️ 高清需要 |\n28: | 👀 **数据追踪** | 播放/点赞/收藏统计、数据追踪、多视频对比（支持 YouTube） | ❌ |\n29: | 📝 **字幕提取** | 字幕下载、格式转换（SRT/ASS/VTT/TXT）、多语言、字幕合并 | ❌ |\n30: | ▶️ **视频播放** | 播放地址获取、弹幕抓取、分P/播放列表信息 | ⚠️ 高清需要 |\n31: | 📤 **视频发布** | 上传投稿、定时发布、草稿管理、编辑/删除视频 | ✅ 必须 |\n32: \n33: ## 🚀 快速开始\n34: \n35: ### 环境要求\n36: \n37: - **Python** >= 3.8\n38: - **ffmpeg**（可选，用于合并视频/音频流）\n39: \n40: ### 安装依赖\n41: \n42: ```bash\n43: git clone https://github.com/wscats/bilibili-all-in-one.git\n44: cd bilibili-all-in-one\n45: pip install -r requirements.txt\n46: ```\n47: \n48: ### 30 秒上手\n49: \n50: ```python\n51: import asyncio\n52: from main import BilibiliAllInOne\n53: \n54: app = BilibiliAllInOne()\n55: \n56: async def main():\n57:     # 获取 B站热门视频\n58:     hot = await app.execute(\"hot_monitor\", \"get_hot\", page_size=5)\n59:     print(hot)\n60: \n61: asyncio.run(main())\n62: ```\n63: \n64: ## ⚙️ 配置认证\n65: \n66: 部分功能（高清下载、视频发布等）需要 B站登录凭据。支持三种配置方式：\n67: \n68: ### 方式一：环境变量（推荐）\n69: \n70: ```bash\n71: export BILIBILI_SESSDATA=\"你的_sessdata\"\n72: export BILIBILI_BILI_JCT=\"你的_bili_jct\"\n73: export BILIBILI_BUVID3=\"你的_buvid3\"\n74: ```\n75: \n76: ### 方式二：凭据文件\n77: \n78: 创建 `credentials.json`：\n79: \n80: ```json\n81: {\n82:   \"sessdata\": \"你的_sessdata\",\n83:   \"bili_jct\": \"你的_bili_jct\",\n84:   \"buvid3\": \"你的_buvid3\"\n85: }\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ### 方式三：代码直接传入\n89: \n90: ```python\n91: app = BilibiliAllInOne(\n92:     sessdata=\"你的_sessdata\",\n93:     bili_jct=\"你的_bili_jct\",\n94:     buvid3=\"你的_buvid3\",\n95: )\n96: ```\n97: \n98: > 💡 **如何获取 Cookie？** 登录 [bilibili.com](https://www.bilibili.com) → 按 F12 打开开发者工具 → Application → Cookies → 复制 `SESSDATA`、`bili_jct`、`buvid3` 的值。\n99: \n100: ---\n101: \n102: ## 📚 使用方式\n103: \n104: ### 命令行（CLI）\n105: \n106: ```bash\n107: python main.py <模块名> <操作> [参数JSON]\n108: ```\n109: \n110: ### Python API\n111: \n112: ```python\n113: import asyncio\n114: from main import BilibiliAllInOne\n115: \n116: app = BilibiliAllInOne()\n117: result = asyncio.run(app.execute(\"模块名\", \"操作\", 参数=值))\n118: ```\n119: \n120: ---\n121: \n122: ## 🔥 模块详解\n123: \n124: ### 1. 热门监控 (`hot_monitor`)\n125: \n126: 实时监控 B站热门视频与话题趋势。\n127: \n128: | 操作 | 说明 | 参数 |\n129: |---|---|---|\n130: | `get_hot` | 获取热门视频列表 | `page`, `page_size` |\n131: | `get_trending` | 获取热搜话题 | `limit` |\n132: | `get_weekly` | 获取每周必看榜 | `number`（期数，可选） |\n133: | `get_rank` | 获取分区排行榜 | `category`, `limit` |\n134: \n135: **支持的分区：** `all`、`anime`、`music`、`dance`、`game`、`tech`、`life`、`food`、`car`、`fashion`、`entertainment`、`movie`、`tv`\n136: \n137: ```bash\n138: # 获取前10个热门视频\n139: python main.py hot_monitor get_hot '{\"page_size\": 10}'\n140: \n141: # 获取游戏区排行榜\n142: python main.py hot_monitor get_rank '{\"category\": \"game\", \"limit\": 10}'\n143: \n144: # 获取本周必看\n145: python main.py hot_monitor get_weekly\n146: \n147: # 获取热搜话题\n148: python main.py hot_monitor get_trending '{\"limit\": 5}'\n149: ```\n150: \n151: ```python\n152: # Python API\n153: result = await app.execute(\"hot_monitor\", \"get_hot\", page_size=10)\n154: result = await app.execute(\"hot_monitor\", \"get_rank\", category=\"game\", limit=10)\n155: result = await app.execute(\"hot_monitor\", \"get_weekly\")\n156: result = await app.execute(\"hot_monitor\", \"get_trending\", limit=5)\n157: ```\n158: \n159: ---\n160: \n161: ### 2. 视频下载 (`downloader`)\n162: \n163: 支持多清晰度、多格式下载，可批量操作。\n164: \n165: | 操作 | 说明 | 参数 |\n166: |---|---|---|\n167: | `get_info` | 获取视频信息 | `url` |\n168: | `get_formats` | 列出可用画质/格式 | `url` |\n169: | `download` | 下载单个视频 | `url`, `quality`, `output_dir`, `format`, `page` |\n170: | `batch_download` | 批量下载多个视频 | `urls`, `quality`, `output_dir`, `format` |\n171: \n172: **清晰度选项：** `360p` · `480p` · `720p` · `1080p`（默认）· `1080p+` · `4k`\n173: \n174: **格式选项：** `mp4`（默认）· `flv` · `mp3`（仅音频）\n175: \n176: ```bash\n177: # 获取视频信息\n178: python main.py downloader get_info '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n179: \n180: # 下载 1080p MP4\n181: python main.py downloader download '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"quality\": \"1080p\"}'\n182: \n183: # 提取音频\n184: python main.py downloader download '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"format\": \"mp3\"}'\n185: \n186: # 批量下载\n187: python main.py downloader batch_download '{\"urls\": [\"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"BV1yy411c8nE\"], \"quality\": \"720p\"}'\n188: ```\n189: \n190: ```python\n191: # Python API\n192: info = await app.execute(\"downloader\", \"get_info\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n193: result = await app.execute(\"downloader\", \"download\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\", quality=\"1080p\")\n194: result = await app.execute(\"downloader\", \"batch_download\", urls=[\"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"BV1yy411c8nE\"])\n195: ```\n196: \n197: ---\n198: \n199: ### 3. 数据追踪 (`watcher`)\n200: \n201: 追踪 B站和 YouTube 视频的互动数据，支持多视频对比。\n202: \n203: | 操作 | 说明 | 参数 |\n204: |---|---|---|\n205: | `watch` | 获取视频详细信息 | `url` |\n206: | `get_stats` | 获取当前互动数据 | `url` |\n207: | `track` | 持续追踪数据变化 | `url`, `interval`（分钟）, `duration`（小时） |\n208: | `compare` | 对比多个视频数据 | `urls` |\n209: \n210: **支持平台：**\n211: - **B站**：`https://www.bilibili.com/video/BVxxxxxx` 或 `BVxxxxxx`\n212: - **YouTube**：`https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xxxxx` 或 `https://youtu.be/xxxxx`\n213: \n214: ```bash\n215: # 查看视频详情\n216: python main.py watcher watch '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n217: \n218: # 获取互动数据\n219: python main.py watcher get_stats '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n220: \n221: # 每30分钟追踪一次，持续12小时\n222: python main.py watcher track '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"interval\": 30, \"duration\": 12}'\n223: \n224: # 对比多个视频\n225: python main.py watcher compare '{\"urls\": [\"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"BV1yy411c8nE\"]}'\n226: \n227: # YouTube 视频也支持\n228: python main.py watcher watch '{\"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ\"}'\n229: ```\n230: \n231: ```python\n232: # Python API\n233: stats = await app.execute(\"watcher\", \"get_stats\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n234: comparison = await app.execute(\"watcher\", \"compare\", urls=[\"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"BV1yy411c8nE\"])\n235: youtube_info = await app.execute(\"watcher\", \"watch\", url=\"https://youtu.be/dQw4w9WgXcQ\")\n236: ```\n237: \n238: ---\n239: \n240: ### 4. 字幕提取 (`subtitle`)\n241: \n242: 下载和处理 B站视频字幕，支持多语言和多格式。\n243: \n244: | 操作 | 说明 | 参数 |\n245: |---|---|---|\n246: | `list` | 列出可用字幕 | `url` |\n247: | `download` | 下载字幕 | `url`, `language`, `format`, `output_dir` |\n248: | `convert` | 转换字幕格式 | `input_path`, `output_format`, `output_dir` |\n249: | `merge` | 合并多个字幕文件 | `input_paths`, `output_path`, `output_format` |\n250: \n251: **支持格式：** `srt`（默认）· `ass` · `vtt` · `txt` · `json`\n252: \n253: **支持语言：** `zh-CN`（默认）· `en` · `ja` 以及视频提供的其他语言\n254: \n255: ```bash\n256: # 列出可用字幕\n257: python main.py subtitle list '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n258: \n259: # 下载中文字幕（SRT格式）\n260: python main.py subtitle download '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"language\": \"zh-CN\", \"format\": \"srt\"}'\n261: \n262: # 下载英文字幕（ASS格式）\n263: python main.py subtitle download '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"language\": \"en\", \"format\": \"ass\"}'\n264: \n265: # 格式转换：SRT → VTT\n266: python main.py subtitle convert '{\"input_path\": \"./subtitles/video.srt\", \"output_format\": \"vtt\"}'\n267: \n268: # 合并多个字幕\n269: python main.py subtitle merge '{\"input_paths\": [\"part1.srt\", \"part2.srt\"], \"output_path\": \"merged.srt\"}'\n270: ```\n271: \n272: ```python\n273: # Python API\n274: subs = await app.execute(\"subtitle\", \"list\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n275: result = await app.execute(\"subtitle\", \"download\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\", language=\"zh-CN\", format=\"srt\")\n276: result = await app.execute(\"subtitle\", \"convert\", input_path=\"video.srt\", output_format=\"vtt\")\n277: ```\n278: \n279: ---\n280: \n281: ### 5. 视频播放 (`player`)\n282: \n283: 获取播放地址、弹幕数据和播放列表信息。\n284: \n285: | 操作 | 说明 | 参数 |\n286: |---|---|---|\n287: | `play` | 获取完整播放信息 | `url`, `quality`, `page` |\n288: | `get_playurl` | 获取直接播放地址 | `url`, `quality`, `page` |\n289: | `get_danmaku` | 获取弹幕数据 | `url`, `page`, `segment` |\n290: | `get_playlist` | 获取分P/播放列表信息 | `url` |\n291: \n292: **弹幕类型：**\n293: \n294: | 模式 | 说明 |\n295: |:---:|---|\n296: | 1 | 滚动弹幕（从右到左） |\n297: | 4 | 底部固定弹幕 |\n298: | 5 | 顶部固定弹幕 |\n299: \n300: ```bash\n301: # 获取播放信息\n302: python main.py player play '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"quality\": \"1080p\"}'\n303: \n304: # 获取播放地址\n305: python main.py player get_playurl '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"quality\": \"720p\"}'\n306: \n307: # 获取弹幕\n308: python main.py player get_danmaku '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n309: \n310: # 获取分P列表\n311: python main.py player get_playlist '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n312: \n313: # 播放多P视频的第3P\n314: python main.py player play '{\"url\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"quality\": \"1080p\", \"page\": 3}'\n315: ```\n316: \n317: ```python\n318: # Python API\n319: play_info = await app.execute(\"player\", \"play\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\", quality=\"1080p\")\n320: danmaku = await app.execute(\"player\", \"get_danmaku\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n321: playlist = await app.execute(\"player\", \"get_playlist\", url=\"BV1xx411c7mD\")\n322: ```\n323: \n324: ---\n325: \n326: ### 6. 视频发布 (`publisher`)\n327: \n328: 上传视频到 B站，支持定时发布和草稿管理。\n329: \n330: > ⚠️ **此模块所有操作均需要登录认证**\n331: \n332: | 操作 | 说明 | 参数 |\n333: |---|---|---|\n334: | `upload` | 上传并发布视频 | `file_path`, `title`, `description`, `tags`, `category`, `cover_path` |\n335: | `draft` | 保存为草稿 | `file_path`, `title`, `description`, `tags`, `category` |\n336: | `schedule` | 定时发布 | `file_path`, `title`, `schedule_time`, `description`, `tags` |\n337: | `edit` | 编辑已发布视频 | `bvid`, `title`, `description`, `tags`, `cover_path` |\n338: | `delete` | 删除视频 | `bvid` |\n339: \n340: **上传参数说明：**\n341: \n342: | 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n343: |---|---|---|---|\n344: | `file_path` | string | *必填* | 视频文件路径 |\n345: | `title` | string | *必填* | 视频标题（最长 80 字） |\n346: | `description` | string | `\"\"` | 视频简介（最长 2000 字） |\n347: | `tags` | string[] | `[\"bilibili\"]` | 标签（最多 12 个，每个最长 20 字） |\n348: | `category` | string | `\"171\"` | 分区 TID |\n349: | `cover_path` | string | `null` | 封面图片路径（JPG/PNG） |\n350: | `no_reprint` | int | `1` | 1=自制，0=转载 |\n351: | `open_elec` | int | `0` | 1=开启充电，0=关闭 |\n352: \n353: ```bash\n354: # 上传并发布\n355: python main.py publisher upload '{\"file_path\": \"./video.mp4\", \"title\": \"我的视频\", \"description\": \"Hello World\", \"tags\": [\"测试\", \"演示\"]}'\n356: \n357: # 保存为草稿\n358: python main.py publisher draft '{\"file_path\": \"./video.mp4\", \"title\": \"草稿视频\"}'\n359: \n360: # 定时发布\n361: python main.py publisher schedule '{\"file_path\": \"./video.mp4\", \"title\": \"定时视频\", \"schedule_time\": \"2025-12-31T20:00:00+08:00\"}'\n362: \n363: # 编辑视频信息\n364: python main.py publisher edit '{\"bvid\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\", \"title\": \"新标题\", \"tags\": [\"更新\"]}'\n365: \n366: # 删除视频\n367: python main.py publisher delete '{\"bvid\": \"BV1xx411c7mD\"}'\n368: ```\n369: \n370: ```python\n371: # Python API（需要认证）\n372: app = BilibiliAllInOne(sessdata=\"xxx\", bili_jct=\"xxx\", buvid3=\"xxx\")\n373: \n374: result = await app.execute(\"publisher\", \"upload\",\n375:     file_path=\"./video.mp4\",\n376:     title=\"我的视频\",\n377:     description=\"通过 bilibili-all-in-one 发布\",\n378:     tags=[\"python\", \"bilibili\"],\n379: )\n380: ```\n381: \n382: ---\n383: \n384: ## 🔒 安全说明\n385: \n386: ### 凭据处理\n387: \n388: | 关注点 | 说明 |\n389: |---|---|\n390: | **需要哪些凭据？** | `SESSDATA`、`bili_jct`、`buvid3` — B站浏览器 Cookie |\n391: | **哪些功能需要认证？** | 视频发布（上传/编辑/删除/定时/草稿）、1080p+/4K 下载 |\n392: | **哪些功能无需认证？** | 热门监控、标准画质下载、字幕获取、弹幕抓取、数据查看 |\n393: | **凭据发送到哪里？** | **仅限** B站官方 API（`api.bilibili.com`、`member.bilibili.com`），全部 HTTPS |\n394: | **是否持久化到磁盘？** | **否** — 除非你主动调用 `auth.save_to_file()`，凭据默认仅存在于内存 |\n395: | **保存文件权限** | `0600`（仅所有者可读写） |\n396: \n397: ### 网络端点\n398: \n399: | 域名 | 用途 |\n400: |---|---|\n401: | `api.bilibili.com` | 视频信息、统计、热门、字幕、弹幕、播放地址 |\n402: | `member.bilibili.com` | 视频发布（上传、编辑、删除） |\n403: | `upos-sz-upcdnbda2.bilivideo.com` | 视频文件上传 CDN |\n404: | `www.bilibili.com` | 网页数据抓取备用 |\n405: | `www.youtube.com` | YouTube 视频元数据获取（oEmbed API，无需认证） |\n406: \n407: ### 安全建议\n408: \n409: 1. 🧪 **使用测试账号** — 请勿使用主账号 Cookie 进行测试\n410: 2. 🔒 **优先使用内存凭据** — 通过环境变量或代码参数传入，避免保存到文件\n411: 3. 📁 **如需保存凭据** — 使用 `auth.save_to_file()`（自动设置 0600 权限），用完后及时删除\n412: 4. 🐳 **隔离运行** — 建议在容器/虚拟环境中运行，并监控网络流量\n413: 5. 🌐 **所有请求仅发往 B站官方域名**，无第三方遥测或数据收集\n414: 6. ❌ **本工具不会将你的凭据发送至任何非 B站的第三方服务**\n415: \n416: ---\n417: \n418: ## 📁 项目结构\n419: \n420: ```\n421: bilibili-all-in-one/\n422: ├── skill.json                      # Skill 配置与参数 Schema\n423: ├── skill.md                        # Skill 英文文档\n424: ├── README.md                       # 中文说明文档（本文件）\n425: ├── requirements.txt                # Python 依赖\n426: ├── main.py                         # 入口文件，统一的 BilibiliAllInOne 类\n427: ├── src/\n428: │   ├── __init__.py                 # 包导出\n429: │   ├── auth.py                     # 认证与凭据管理\n430: │   ├── utils.py                    # 共享工具函数、API 常量\n431: │   ├── hot_monitor.py              # 🔥 热门监控模块\n432: │   ├── downloader.py               # ⬇️ 视频下载模块\n433: │   ├── watcher.py                  # 👀 数据追踪模块\n434: │   ├── subtitle.py                 # 📝 字幕提取模块\n435: │   ├── player.py                   # ▶️ 视频播放模块\n436: │   └── publisher.py                # 📤 视频发布模块\n437: └── tests/\n438:     ├── __init__.py\n439:     └── test_all_skill_examples.py  # 27 个完整测试用例\n440: ```\n441: \n442: ## 🧬 技能来源\n443: \n444: 本项目整合了以下 6 个独立 Skill 的功能：\n445: \n446: | 原始 Skill | 来源 | 整合为 |\n447: |---|---|---|\n448: | bilibili-hot-monitor | [Jacobzwj/bilibili-hot-monitor](https://clawhub.ai/Jacobzwj/bilibili-hot-monitor) | `hot_monitor` |\n449: | bililidownloader | [caiyundc880518/bililidownloader](https://clawhub.ai/caiyundc880518/bililidownloader) | `downloader` |\n450: | bilibili-youtube-watcher | [donnycui/bilibili-youtube-watcher](https://clawhub.ai/donnycui/bilibili-youtube-watcher) | `watcher` |\n451: | bilibili-subtitle-download-skill | [DavinciEvans/bilibili-subtitle-download-skill](https://clawhub.ai/DavinciEvans/bilibili-subtitle-download-skill) | `subtitle` |\n452: | bilibili-player | [e421083458/bilibili-player](https://clawhub.ai/e421083458/bilibili-player) | `player` |\n453: | bilibili-video-publish | [Johnnyxu820/bilibili-video-publish](https://clawhub.ai/Johnnyxu820/bilibili-video-publish) | `publisher` |\n454: \n455: ## 📦 统一返回格式\n456: \n457: 所有操作返回统一的 JSON 结构：\n458: \n459: **成功：**\n460: \n461: ```json\n462: {\n463:   \"success\": true,\n464:   \"...\": \"操作相关的数据字段\"\n465: }\n466: ```\n467: \n468: **失败：**\n469: \n470: ```json\n471: {\n472:   \"success\": false,\n473:   \"message\": \"错误描述信息\"\n474: }\n475: ```\n476: \n477: ## 🧪 运行测试\n478: \n479: ```bash\n480: # 运行全部 27 个测试\n481: python -m unittest tests.test_all_skill_examples -v\n482: ```\n483: \n484: ## 📄 许可证\n485: \n486: [MIT](LICENSE)\n\n(End of file - total 486 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <h1 align=\"center\">🎬 Bilibili All-in-One</h1>\n  <p align=\"center\">一站式 B站工具箱 — 热门监控 · 视频下载 · 数据追踪 · 字幕提取 · 视频播放 · 投稿发布</p>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/python-%3E%3D3.8-blue?logo=python&logoColor=white\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.9-orange\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/platform-Bilibili%20%7C%20YouTube-pink\" />\n</p>\n\n---\n\n## 📖 简介\n\n**Bilibili All-in-One** 是一个综合性的 B站工具包，将 6 个独立的 B站技能整合为一个统一的 Skill，提供从热门监控到视频投稿的全链路能力。\n\n支持作为 **AI Agent 技能**、**命令行工具** 或 **Python 库** 使用。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\capability-library\\skill-library\\bilibili-all-in-one-1.0.12\\README.md","time":{"start":1778730042385,"end":1778730042400}},"id":"prt_e249282ba00180E026Yq1zGO7M","sessionID":"ses_1db6e3a79ffefCAEjX4WmRwXGO","messageID":"msg_e249265ee001acJZjevoyJXRf6"}}
